| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1442 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3e60c51b-b0a1-5f1d-9324-e4d03b3f48f0"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
